Gantry-Plugins-Session version 0.03
===================================

This module provides a way to create and track sessions for the Gantry
framework.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Gantry
  Gantry::Plugins::Cache
  Crypt::CBC
  
